        <div style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#ffc107 15%,var(--bg-color));border:1px solid #ffc107;border-radius:4px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:0.88em;">
            <strong>⚠️ Migration Status:</strong> This master plan is being migrated from text-based files to the DB-driven planning system.
