        <h2>Planning System Migration - Implementation Plan</h2>
        <p style="background: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0;">
            <strong>Overview:</strong> This implementation plan outlines the migration from a text-based planning system to a dynamic, database-driven application with role-based access control, project-documentation linking, and comprehensive audit trails.
        </p>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <button onclick="createProject()" style="padding: 10px 20px; background: var(--primary-color); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;">
